Following is a summary of the Aug.
construction spending report from the Commerce Department.  NOTE: Percents are month over month unless otherwise stated.
Residential construction includes home improvements.
Three month annualized calculations are the latest three
months average compared to the previous three months average.
Home Improvement is calculated by Bloomberg.  SOURCE: U.S. Commerce Department.     http://www.census.gov/constructionspending   To contact the reporter on this story:
